A '''Seggor''' was a large [[Ocean/Legends|oceanic]] predator native to the [[Water/Legends|waters]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]]. They were revered by the [[Quarren/Legends|Quarren]], who respected them for the strength they possessed. It was a common given name for male Quarren.

